<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank You for Your Enquiry</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .email-body h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .email-body p {
      margin: 16px 0;
      color: #666666;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .info-box strong {
      color: #333333;
      display: inline-block;
      min-width: 80px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    .email-footer p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container {
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
      }
      .email-header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .email-header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .info-box {
        padding: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1><%= @site_name %></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <h2>Thank you for your enquiry!</h2>

      <p>Dear <%= @enquiry.name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for contacting us. We have received your enquiry and will get back to you as soon as possible, typically within 1-2 business days.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Your Enquiry Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @enquiry.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @enquiry.email %></p>
        <% if @enquiry.phone.present? %>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= @enquiry.phone %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if @enquiry.company.present? %>
          <p><strong>Company:</strong> <%= @enquiry.company %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if @enquiry.subject.present? %>
          <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= @enquiry.subject %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if @enquiry.message.present? %>
          <p><strong>Message:</strong><br><%= simple_format(@enquiry.message) %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any additional questions in the meantime, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= @site_name %> Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> <%= @site_name %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
